features: Responsive Fingerprint Door Lock: Equipped with a 360° biometric fingerprint sensor, the keyless entry deadbolt can recognize your finger in just 0.3s and unlock your door in 1 second. No more fumbling with your bag or worrying about forgetting your key. Your Finger is Your Key!

6-in-1 Smart Lock Deadbolt: Fingerprint, IC card, APP, passcode, Apple Watch and keys. This digital door lock provides multiple unlocking methods. You can enter 50 fingerprints, remotely generate 250 PIN codes, share keys and authorize administrators anywhere. Everything you need in 1 safe and secure smart lock. If you pair it with the G2 Gateway (sold separately), you can lock/unlock your door with Alexa or Google Assistant and unlock it remotely via the APP.

One-Touch Locking & Auto Lock: Just press the # button on the keypad for 2s to quickly lock the door. You can enable the auto-lock feature and set the timer from 10-900s! No worry about forgetting to lock the door. The automatic door lock is always your backup. Add random numbers before or after your correct passcode to protect it from prying eyes. Keep you safety and peace of mind in one secure lock.

Durable & High Quality: Unlike those electric door locks that only last 3 months, TEEHO electronic door lock has a battery life of up to 1 year. A low battery alert reminds you to replace the battery in time. Our door lock with keypads is IP54 waterproof for outdoor use and ANSI Class 3 certified, with a rugged alloy construction ensuring it can handle any weather from -31°F to 151°F. Crafted for performance and reliability in any season, it's the perfect choice for your home.

Easy Installation & Warranty: With only a screwdriver, you can have it up and running; no need for a locksmith or extra drilling. TEEHO offers 1-year warranty and lifetime technical support. Please do not hesitate to contact us if you need our help.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: TEEHO Door Lock, Unlock Smart Life 6-in-1 Keyless Entry Door Lock: Unlock by Apple Watch, Fingerprint, PIN codes, APP, IC Cards, Keys

Apple Watch Unlock Connect with bluetooth to achieve the easy unlock via your Apple Watch. Note: Please separately download the DDlock on the Apple Watch after successfully pair the DDlock with your smart lock. Fingerprint Fast recognition in 0.3 seconds, up to 50 fingerprints, fingerprint door lock bring you convenient life. Note: Fingerprints can only open the door, not lock it. Please keep your finger dry and clean. PIN Codes 250 PIN codes meet your needs. Please note that the PIN code only unlocks the door, not locks it. APP Control Touch to unlock, hold 3 seconds to lock the door. Easy control of your smart lock! FOB Card Swipe your card and open the door easily. Keys 2 keys as your emergency backup! Don't worry about running out of battery.

Suitable for Families, Apartment, and Airbnb Up to 250 User Codes Remotely generate a variety of PIN codes to unlock your door effortlessly. With 250 user codes available, individuals can easily personalize their unique passcodes. No need for complex programming. Convenience & Safety One-Time Passcode Anywhere and anytime, you can remotely generate a one-time passcode that is automatically deleted after use. This feature is ideal for granting temporary access to neighbors, repairmen, pet sitters, and more. Low Battery Alert 1 Year Long Battery Life Low energy consumption, only 4 AA batteries can be used for up to 1 year. You need to replace the batteries if you hear 3 beeps and 3 red light flashes when unlocking. Smart & Easier Life Auto Lock & One-Touch Locking Forget to Lock the Door? Don't worry. The auto-lock feature is the ideal solution. TEEHO smart deadbolt allows you to set the auto-lock feature and to customize the delay time from 10-900s. Long press the # button for 2s to close the lock. Lock your door easier and faster. Sturdy and Durability Works Well in All Weather Conditions The keyless entry door lock is IP54 waterproof and can operate from -31°F to 151°F. Our digital lock can keep your home safe in different weather, no matter whether it is chilly winter, hot summer, or rainy day. Protect Your Privacy & Safety Anti-peeping PIN Codes Safeguard your PIN codes from prying eyes by adding random digits to your password. This extra layer of security helps ensure your codes stay private and secure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install, works great, looks nice
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice lock for the money.It was super easy to install. About 5 minutes.App was easy to setup. Easy to add users and their fingerprints.Family loves it!They don't always appreciate all my smart home hobby toys. But they like this one. They like getting in the house quickly, without having to dig for keys or ring the doorbell.We added the optional gateway hub that let's you connect to your Wi-Fi router and unlock remotely. That is handy if you have family or guests arrive and you happen to be out running errands or something.I can imagine it would be great for a rental situation too. Just create temporary pass codes that expire on a certain date. No worries about forgetting to delete it later.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Product & Easy to install.
reviews.reviewText: Completely Love it! I love the fingerprint option & how it locks automatically after so many seconds (customizable). You do have to order a separate piece (D2 device) to operate independently on phone app via WiFi if not in close proximity. Great value overall! Works better than my previous lock (kwikset).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought two of these. They were very easy to install and program. I have mine to accept the fingerprint feature and it works every time just by tapping the pad. The only issue I have is that they are not easy to link to Alexa. I think I need a special hub to get it to talk to Alexa. If I could get it to connect, I would give it 5 stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Cheap and glitchy
reviews.reviewText: Not impressed. Keypad not responsive. Hard to get numbers to press. It wouldn’t register fingerprint or fob. Returned. You also have to drill a hold above the deadbolt to mount it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love the options of keypad code, fingerprint or key.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: For the price and the features that come with the lock is great. I would highly recommend you get the gateway for it as it will be able to tell you in real time when someone accessed the door from the outside. I wish there was an option to show if someone unlocked it from the inside. Other then that great product and easy to install.

reviews.reviewText: Love this item works great just install is a bit of a process but other than that great product !

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Loved it while it worked
reviews.reviewText: Edit: the company reached out and sent a replacement! Working great! Love it! I have 9 kids so we don’t need 10000 keys! Hopefully it lasts longer.Was the perfect lock while it worked. After 3 to 4 months the lock stopped working. I got locked in my house. Could not even manually turn the lock. Emailed. Haven’t gotten any advice that helped. It was obvious from correspondence with the company they did not actually read the email I sent.
